Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.93,1:11:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Joe, you better quit eating those things too much, you're going to get way too much.\NHe reminds me of a joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.50,1:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for it.\NThis guy, this guy, Pete, his name is Pete.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.59,1:12:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything goes wrong with his life.\NHis car breaks down.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.61,1:12:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,His business fails.\NHis health is bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.61,1:12:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife leaves him.\NHe stands out on the sidewalk and he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.30,1:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,God, God.\NWhy me?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.30,1:12:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And a voice comes out of the heavens and says,\NI don't know, Pete, there's something about you that just pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.84,1:12:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually, you told that joke yesterday?\NWhen he asked the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.84,1:12:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be Pete then.\NAlright, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.97,1:13:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I changed the name to Pete.\NMaybe you won't recognize the joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.97,1:13:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just to make, he wants to know if whoever is speaking to him is a higher being or is he tapping into his thoughts?\NWell, you're tapping into intuition, intuition and non-logical styles of understanding things, comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.69,1:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's a certain advantage to it, yes.\NYou know, because if logic was sufficient, you wouldn't be working on a problem or, you know, you would have had it solved already.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.92,1:13:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NBecause what you're getting at right now is that it's not non-scientific, it's not logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.75,1:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from some kind of voice, some kind of choreography.\NSo, you're saying that it has an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.75,1:14:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you're getting the answer.\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.51,1:14:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very long, could be a long question.\NShe had three very profound experiences throughout her life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.06,1:14:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At age four, she was in a room and through a tiny window she was looking outside.\NAnd she saw a golden light.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.27,1:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And then with that instant, she acquired some supernatural abilities.\NAt age four?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.10,1:14:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At age four.\NAt age four.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.10,1:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Supernatural, what does that mean?\NSee through people and able to read people's mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.10,1:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,At age four?\NYeah, and yes, after that moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.65,1:14:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NThen she saw a person sitting next to her and she knew that it was a person from her past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.65,1:14:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.\NHer past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.65,1:15:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a Buddhist monk.\NAnd she then came a thought asking, which one is me?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.90,1:15:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This person or that person?\NAnd then the answer said, only consciousness is you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.73,1:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then a very sharp, almost screaming voice said, what am I?\NAnd intuitively she knew that this voice will dominate my life from now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.14,1:15:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first experience.\NAnd second experience happened at age seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.17,1:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At age seven or eight on a spring day.\NAnd she felt a sunshine on her back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.10,1:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And she knew that she was entering the world of enlightenment.\NAnd from then on, she knew intuitively all the Buddhist teachings because she was probably a Buddhist in her past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.40,1:16:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is this non-verbal knowledge.\NNon-verbal knowingness that the universe itself is love.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.23,1:16:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And she saw how petty human love is compared to that infinite love.\NAnd all the world is a smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.52,1:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,When a flower blooms, she sees a smile there.\NAnd then she said, then question came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.97,1:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she thought I came here just after I passed the level 600.\NAnd why am I not living as an enlightened person?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.97,1:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And her understanding is, I experienced enlightenment but a mind attached to it.\NThat was the first thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.28,1:17:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again.\NAnd then she was, she thought that she passed the level 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.96,1:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThen her question was.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.96,1:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, hold on.\NShe did transcend level 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.50,1:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NSo?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.01,1:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then her question is, why am I not living?\NAs an enlightened person.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.01,1:17:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she not leaving?\NWhat's enlightenment got to do with leaving?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.01,1:17:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotional.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.01,1:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Living a life.\NLiving a life as an enlightened person.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.01,1:17:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThen her answer was, to my enlightened state, a mind was attached.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.35,1:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her answer.\NI experienced union mystica with a mind attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.85,1:17:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words.\NShe's still of mind, not of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.10,1:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still of mind.\NSo her mind was stronger than her spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.38,1:18:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, her mind's controlling.\NShe identifies her reality as the mind instead of spirit?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.18,1:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NThat's her understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.50,1:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her understanding.\NOf why she's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.50,1:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bad understanding.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.50,1:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The third experience happened at age 13.\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.50,1:18:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's two words, positive and negative.\NAnd she forgot all about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.61,1:18:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And she spent her past 50 years experiencing the whole gamut of emotions below 200.\NFrom 20 to 175.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.61,1:18:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NAnd then she did 12 steps group for eight years.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.61,1:18:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Through that, she regained the memory of those three experiences, profound experiences.\NAnd the question she's asking is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.61,1:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she really wants that all her struggle throughout 50 years, spiritual struggle.\NReally want that to come to a spiritual fruition.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.18,1:19:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is not able to do it.\NSo asking for your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.18,1:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she mean by fruition?\NShe wants to.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.28,1:19:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's still going through emotions below 200.\NShe wants to get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.28,1:19:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then she wasn't over 600.\NShe could have been in a past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.84,1:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in a past life she.\NMight have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.35,1:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NWe have permission to ask where she's at now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.84,1:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's over 200, 400, 500.\NNow she's trying to figure things out in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.22,1:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NSo she's trying to understand intellectually in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.81,1:20:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She should stop trying to understand it intellectually.\NBecause no matter what she thinks, it's going to be nonsense anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.89,1:20:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to figure it out intellectually.\NStop trying to manipulate your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.90,1:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it be what it is.\NIt's too much self-consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.81,1:20:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be and stop thinking about it.\NAnd she also said.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.81,1:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NShe understood that those experiences inflated her spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.81,1:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And she thinks now that is over.\NAlmost she's feeling humility now.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.81,1:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.81,1:21:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So then asking for your help.\NThese experiences, these profound experiences inflated her spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.81,1:21:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NOh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.81,1:21:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NThe spiritual ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.81,1:21:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Got inflated.\NMade something out of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.94,1:21:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.94,1:21:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it stopped doing that.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.94,1:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThe levels of those experiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.94,1:21:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know.\NWhat experiences?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.94,1:21:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The three profound experiences.\NThe three experiences she had.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.94,1:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The levels.\NThis is too complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.61,1:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too complicated.\NToo complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.81,1:21:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the first experience?\NWas the light she saw at four.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.81,1:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The light she saw at age four.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.81,1:21:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Was over 600, 700, 650.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.85,1:21:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next experience?\NThe next experience was.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.77,1:21:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Love.\NThe.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.77,1:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In which she got the understanding that.\NEntire universe itself is a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.06,1:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NSo that calibrated over 700.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.69,1:22:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,750.\NAbout 700, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.96,1:22:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NThat's number two.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.22,1:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's number three?\NTwo different.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.22,1:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Three is.\NTwo words.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.22,1:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two words.\NTwo words.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.22,1:22:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive and negative.\NNegative.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.22,1:22:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Three was what?\NTwo words.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.22,1:22:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive and negative.\NI don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.46,1:22:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's meaningless to me, out of context.\NI would have to look at the context.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.47,1:23:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have to look at the context.\NWhether she has the power to write down all the spiritual experiences she underwent throughout her life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.10,1:23:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether she has the power to write that down.\NWrite it down for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.10,1:23:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For others to look at it.\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.18,1:24:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that could be helpful to others.\NHow is it helpful?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.18,1:24:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know what it means, so what's the message she's going to say?\NI don't know what this means.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.68,1:24:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop thinking about it.\NStop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.43,1:24:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it be what it is.\NWithout thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.43,1:24:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's ruminating.\NShe's ruminating, thinking, judging, processing it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.27,1:24:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it be.\NI make a song.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.34,1:24:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I go, la la la la la la la la la la la.\NThat's all there is to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.22,1:25:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I say, that was a good song, that was a bad song, that was a famous song.\NOh, that's a rerun of a song from a childhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.89,1:25:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a song that signifies the human condition.\NOh, that's a song from the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.89,1:25:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a song.\NThat's all spinning with the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.89,1:25:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NLa la la la la la la la la la.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.89,1:25:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.\NIf there's a song like this, that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.21,1:25:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you hear this song?\NWhat kind of song is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.21,1:25:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No thinking.\NNo talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.21,1:25:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it be what it is.\NLa la la la la la la la la la.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.68,1:25:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom.\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.68,1:25:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.\NNot bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.68,1:25:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just is.\NIs.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.68,1:25:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.\NNot good.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.68,1:25:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad.\NJust is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.68,1:25:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is.\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.42,1:25:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.\NNot bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.67,1:25:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just is.\NIs.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.67,1:25:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good or bad.\NJust as is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.02,1:25:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom, bap, bap, boom, bap, boom, boom, boom, boom, boom, boom.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.27,1:25:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting speed, just to let them be.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.46,1:26:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them be.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.53,1:26:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll directly ask you a question.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.34,1:26:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She speaks English.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.39,1:26:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.\NUm ... It seems like this one is experiencing constant accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.60,1:26:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,conflict at home so and i've been um praying as you said praying um as god's help and um knowledge\Nnot knowledge for god's will and power to carry that out and also uh as for miracle and uh
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.30,1:27:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly trying to uh see it differently and all those things for a couple of years now\Nstressful like how it's more like i'm creating and experiencing more uh conflict with my spouse
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.26,1:27:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,oh your spouse yes yes and the basic uh basic thing\Nis that i'm trying to make sure that i'm not the only one who's having a hard time
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.92,1:27:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and i'm trying to make sure that i'm not the only one who's having a hard time\Nis more like there's a huge differences
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.34,1:27:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,between our belief system,\Nand his belief system is there's no life after death,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.76,1:27:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no God.\NOh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.97,1:27:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I'm coming here almost 10 years,\NI mean, constantly, and every time,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.43,1:27:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's a lot of,\NI mean, this one is creating lots of conflict at home
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.47,1:27:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because of that, and I've been praying,\Nand I don't want to create any more bad karma,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.56,1:27:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I could see his viewpoint, and I understand,\Nand I could feel his pain, and I cannot agree with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.81,1:27:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his pain, what pain?\NHe doesn't believe in God, so what's his pain about?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.30,1:27:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,His pain is that you are a believer in God?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.18,1:28:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His pain is you.\NI'm living, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.43,1:28:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you keep it to yourself?\NI believe in God, I don't care if anybody else agrees with me
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.22,1:28:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,or knows about it, I don't make a,\NI don't stand up and say,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.81,1:28:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a believer in God.\NI don't want us to all believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.64,1:28:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my private inner self.\NHow does that create conflict?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.92,1:28:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he doesn't want me to go away and really,\Nbecause.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.06,1:28:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away where?\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.97,1:28:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.\NOh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.65,1:28:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And spiritual practice.\NOh, I see, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.34,1:28:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And trying to prevent him from.\NOh, oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.18,1:28:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Showing her religious beliefs.\NWell, yeah, so you tell him,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.34,1:28:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to accept your atheism,\Nand you, in return, you must accept my theism.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.69,1:28:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't like it,\Nthen you must live with somebody else, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.30,1:28:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.38,1:28:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm praying for, what is the highest good,\NI mean, either should I stay with this guy or no?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.61,1:28:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm praying for a couple of years now,\Nand I don't get any answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.22,1:28:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean.\NYou will.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.27,1:29:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You will.\NI know, and I believe that, but it's.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.96,1:29:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the answer you're getting is to live with it.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.94,1:29:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Patience.\NTolerance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.07,1:29:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to have tolerance.\NTolerance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.73,1:29:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They both have to have tolerance, you know.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.44,1:29:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tolerance for each other's wisdom.\NYeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.73,1:29:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.\NWell, I don't want to control him,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.00,1:29:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes, it feels like he's,\Nit seems like he's a better human being than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.02,1:29:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's a very respectable guy in some way,\Nand he's very responsible, and I respect that,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.03,1:29:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe I, I don't know.\NIt's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.85,1:29:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.\NYes, and I cannot, anything I could do,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.75,1:30:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but this, I cannot give up.\NI mean, this is my, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.86,1:30:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.\NYeah, but it's, but it seems like it's,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.43,1:30:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the conflict is getting worse, so.\NSo, answer yourself and you pray, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.39,1:31:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he should not stop you.\NActually, he can stop me, but he's getting angry,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.09,1:31:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and creating a lot of conflict at home.\NI mean, he can't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.09,1:31:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he can.\NHe knows that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.67,1:31:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well, but he's not.\NHe's not stopping you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.94,1:31:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't stop you.\NThere's just a question in his mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.15,1:31:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard, but you're inner.\NSo if you can show him your spiritual belief, he will accept.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.46,1:31:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very common for the man to be the businessman, logical, you know,\Nand the woman goes to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.85,1:32:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very common.\NThe woman and the children go to church, and he figures, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.31,1:32:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that's for women and children.\NBecause his mind is on business and logic.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.72,1:32:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the different archetypes that the male and female come from sometimes.\NDoc, do you think you could calibrate,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.47,1:32:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the highest good that I'm leaving him?\NThe highest good that you should leave him?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.43,1:32:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NMake God happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.92,1:32:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that too, yes.\NThat's a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.77,1:32:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't really calibrate a decision like that, no.\NSo the best way is I keep praying.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.89,1:32:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to show him.\NWhy do they have to agree?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.43,1:32:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why they have to agree about it.\NYou have to understand the culture.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.57,1:33:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A Korean man can stop a woman from doing anything they want.\NOh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.43,1:33:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a culture thing.\NHe isn't stopping her, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.47,1:33:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.69,1:33:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's allowing her to be.\NSo the solution is love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.00,1:33:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.02,1:33:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer to it is love.\NIf you love him enough to accept the way he is and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.44,1:33:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to cross over is with love.\NShow him the love in you as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.17,1:33:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThe compromise is via love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.39,1:33:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Without love, you can't solve it.\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.10,1:33:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So love will either solve it or it won't.\NAnd if there's not enough love, then you won't solve it because there isn't enough love.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.10,1:34:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If love is more important than anything else, then you'll stay with it.\NIf other things are more important, then that will dissolve the relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.92,1:34:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So it depends on what you want from a relationship.\NIf I don't find love in a relationship, goodbye relationship.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.72,1:34:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what's a relationship all about?\NIt's all about love.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.43,1:34:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there isn't love, then there's no reason for it.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.57,1:34:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.64,1:34:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.09,1:34:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.98,1:34:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.90,1:34:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Send him over.\NI'll talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.52,1:34:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will.\NI try.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.17,1:34:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have a last question.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.59,1:34:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.\NHe's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.73,1:34:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to take a break either way.\NYeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.44,1:34:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, you take a break?\NYeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.55,1:34:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They may have to go to the bathroom too.\NEverybody may need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.14,1:34:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.52,1:35:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He has two questions.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.43,1:35:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThe first question is, when I was four years old, my family got into a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.75,1:35:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a car accident.\NWhen he was four?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.22,1:35:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NHe was four years old, entire family got into a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.51,1:35:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NEverybody got hurt, but only his mother died.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.68,1:35:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NA few years later, his father got remarried, and he's got a stepmother, and then he divorced again.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.36,1:35:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.02,1:35:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.34,1:35:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.53,1:36:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And after a few years after that, his father got remarried, and he's living with the second stepmother until now.\NHow old is he now?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.31,1:36:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How old is he now?\NHow old is he now?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.84,1:36:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,26.\NThrough these experiences, what sort of karmic understanding he could get from this?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.82,1:36:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The nature of human life, you see, the nature of human life,\Ntakes many forms.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.25,1:36:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are various diversions.\NAnd to accept that, there are multitudinous patterns
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.69,1:37:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of which the conventional ones are only one alternative.\NThere are probably more people living
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.42,1:37:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in unconventional circumstances\Nthan there are in conventional circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.39,1:37:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, what, 50% of marriages end in divorce, 50%.\NSo what's the norm?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.63,1:37:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The norm is to get divorced.\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.97,1:37:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, many times your parents get married two or three times.\NYou know?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.81,1:37:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In America, parents get married two or three times.\NIn America, parents get married two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.02,1:37:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's really his father's karma, too.\NIn fact, this is more related to his father's karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.64,1:38:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The second question.\NI want to live with courage and dignity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.14,1:38:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to follow the teaching of the doctor.\NI want to serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.03,1:38:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To achieve that, I am praying.\NHe wants to live his life with dignity and courage, and he wants to devote his life to
Dialogue: 0,1:38:38.57,1:39:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,your teachings, and what is the best way of doing it?\NThe books all tell you how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.98,1:39:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Through prayer, meditation, and being loving towards all of life.\NAnd to be non-judgmental about things about which you have an aversion, but to not be
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.81,1:39:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,judgmental about things that you have aversion to.\NBut to not be judgmental about things that you have aversion to.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.90,1:39:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that is the way it is for those people and their karma, see?\NBut it's not your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.10,1:39:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean it's wrong, it just means it's not your way.\NI don't believe in blowing up busloads of children.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.61,1:39:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my way, see?\NI don't believe in blowing up busloads of children.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.44,1:40:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in blowing up buses of children, either.\NI believe in aÕÆī and to one of the best ways of living, which is to not be judgmental
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.85,1:40:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,towards it.\NAnd that is sentient, to remain a person, not to have a roots of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.90,1:40:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the same way, to pass on to other people those who come to you with a sense of resentment,\Nto feelness of resentment.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.10,1:40:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For the reason of not having a inner strength.\NThe reason of not having a inner strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.07,1:40:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For the reason of not having a inner strength.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.34,1:40:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still believe in positive actions?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.84,1:40:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in positive actions.\NFor the reason of not having a conscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.30,1:40:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, do you believe in such things?\NFor the reason of not having a conscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.84,1:40:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in positive actions.\NYou see, you see how the, how is the Komodo dragon, the Komodo dragon, one bite and you're
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.52,1:40:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,dead.\NYou don't have to hate the Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.35,1:40:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't put your foot in its cage.\NSo you can respect everything being what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.52,1:41:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hate it.\NYou don't have to agree with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.93,1:41:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You accept that it's part of divine creation.\NAnd people would say, well, why would God create a Komodo dragon?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.18,1:41:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NWho cares?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.18,1:41:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put your foot in there.\NYou see.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.02,1:41:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.21,1:41:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.21,1:41:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.21,1:41:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.21,1:41:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.21,1:41:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.21,1:41:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.21,1:41:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.21,1:41:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.21,1:41:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.21,1:41:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.21,1:41:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.21,1:41:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.21,1:41:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.21,1:41:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.27,1:41:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.61,1:41:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.61,1:42:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,.\NYes. So we need to take a short break. How do we work it now?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.73,1:42:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we will ask your blessings for some people.\NFor the people?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.73,1:42:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby and people, some people with sickness.\NSome people want your healing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.73,1:42:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes, yes.\NAfter the break.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.73,1:42:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay, yes. All right, so now we take a break?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.73,1:42:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.78,1:42:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice, very nice.\NI wish I could have answered some of the questions more fully.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.68,1:42:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, I give thanks for your being here.\NYour being here is like a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.68,1:42:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I love these people here.\NI love the Korean people in general and these people here in particular.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.68,1:42:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.68,1:42:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I bless you in the name of the Lord.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.10,1:43:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful people, yeah.\NWe have some blessings to do at this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.40,1:43:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.\NAnd there is a, if you want to turn around here, there is women that are expecting.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.40,1:43:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.\NAnd they, I don't know if you want to sit down for this, David.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.30,1:43:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.30,1:43:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stand up, we'll stand up.\NWe'll take a, we'll get a sip of water.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.75,1:43:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Little boy who cut class to come.\NLet's see, why are we seeing him?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.03,1:43:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again, just giving this blessing because he wanted to come and.\NOh, God bless you and thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.03,1:43:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.\NThank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.57,1:43:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a hug.\NGood, good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.57,1:43:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.57,1:43:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NHave a good week.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.57,1:44:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.57,1:44:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.57,1:44:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.06,1:44:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.92,1:44:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.57,1:44:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.57,1:44:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the baby.\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.57,1:44:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, sweetheart.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.57,1:44:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Lord, amen.\NWhat a divine being.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.57,1:44:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cute.\NA divine being.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.57,1:44:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?\NHow much?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.57,1:44:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a child of God.\NThat was so good.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.28,1:44:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for such a lovely child.\NOh, God created another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.89,1:44:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried that before.\NIt's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.06,1:44:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God created another one!\NI tried that before with him and he didn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.93,1:45:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he likes you. He loves you, David.\NYes, well, you were created by God, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.02,1:45:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless the baby in your womb. Amen.\NGod's creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.22,1:45:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All creatures are creatures of God.\NSo you hold within your womb the creation of God
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.00,1:45:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have reverence for it\Nand reverence that you have been chosen as a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.17,1:45:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a mother.\NI wasn't chosen by God to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.17,1:46:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You were chosen by God to be a mother.\NYes, otherwise you wouldn't be pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.52,1:46:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And a great blessing.\NHe's a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.61,1:46:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.61,1:46:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know the conflict between North Korea and South Korea.\NOh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.61,1:46:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NSo he's one of the men who are defending.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.26,1:46:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.\NYou're in the army?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.43,1:46:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.43,1:46:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A captain.\NIn the army?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.43,1:46:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.\NOh, very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.09,1:46:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the Navy in World War II.\NWorld War II.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.88,1:46:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, serviceman.\NService.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.17,1:47:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Service is a great thing to experience,\Nto be part of a whole army, part of a whole ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.43,1:47:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great experience.\NGreat experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.01,1:47:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And you make friendships that last many years.\NI was on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.31,1:47:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a small ship, 26.\N26.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.84,1:47:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And after the war, we sent each other cards for many years.\NFor many years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:44.93,1:47:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For 50 years.\NFor 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.25,1:47:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I got Christmas.\NFor years and years.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.25,1:47:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year I got Christmas cards from other crew members.\NAnd gradually as the years went by, the number of cards got fewer and fewer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.65,1:48:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This year I got.\NSay none.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.09,1:49:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This year I didn't get any.\NSo you see the love, the bond, lasts a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.96,1:49:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is a different kind of love than romantic love.\NLove of your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.81,1:49:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a great love.\NIt lasts 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.50,1:49:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThere were several other people that wanted to shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.10,1:49:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NOh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.42,1:49:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.32,1:49:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me whatever you want.\NIt's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.56,1:49:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want, it's fine with me.\NGlad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.56,1:49:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to meet you.\NI'm honored to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.56,1:49:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for being here.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.56,1:49:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
