Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.11,1:54:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,life many of them are the undoing of Karma negative Karma you know so we meet them as best we can\Nvicissitudes of life yeah this is it yes that's a nice jacket I like that jacket would that fit me
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.36,1:54:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that fit me?\NThat would fit me pretty near.
