Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.82,1:55:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThat's nice and warm, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.39,1:55:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.81,1:55:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.\NI'll have to stand on my tiptoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.00,1:55:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There.\NGod bless.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.47,1:55:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asking for his daughter, who's suffering from the illness.\NThe illness.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.72,1:56:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His daughter is having an illness.\NWhat is the illness?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.27,1:56:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuberous sclerosis.\NSome DNA defect.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.18,1:56:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.97,1:56:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.61,1:56:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.68,1:56:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless her.\NAnyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.57,1:56:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She fulfills her destiny that way.\NCan we get rid of some negative karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.44,1:56:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.10,1:56:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fulfilling that.\NThat's.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.65,1:56:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fulfilling that destiny.\NWhatever befalls us, you know, has to do with destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.80,1:57:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And destiny, you know, karma means one's destiny, that all that we have inherited as human beings, you see.\NThrough the undoing of negative karma, we fulfill our destiny and we reach salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.56,1:57:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess salvation, you know.\NAnd to try and accept it with grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.89,1:57:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and accept one's karma\Nwith grace. Yes. That's a nice
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.19,1:57:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,chapter too. I like that one.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.07,1:57:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. God bless you.\NYou have
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.53,1:57:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a smiley face. Smiles.\NGood smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.73,1:57:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That cheers up the world.\NYou smile at people
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.88,1:57:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,when you walk down the street and they go\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.05,1:57:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for smiling.\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:02.88,1:58:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's tall too.\NTall young man.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.96,1:58:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?\N40.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:12.89,1:58:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,40? 40? Yeah.\NOh. I thought he was
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.18,1:58:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,younger than that.\NOkay. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.36,1:58:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have courage.\NYou have courage.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.50,1:58:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. How are you?\NI have a special one for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.02,1:58:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.89,1:59:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is lovely.\NIs this a
Dialogue: 0,1:59:01.14,1:59:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Korean necklace?\NThey can hug me as long as they're gentle about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.53,1:59:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a handsome young man.\NGod bless him.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.84,1:59:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how nice he looks.\NBeautifully dressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.26,1:59:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's lovely. Thank you.\NThank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.31,1:59:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.61,1:59:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NYou told me I'd be able to serve you,
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.07,1:59:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but I love you.\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.39,1:59:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, yes.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.81,1:59:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NOh, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.36,1:59:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these people came such a long way.\NI'm honored by the long trip you made to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:44.85,1:59:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NIsn't that lovely?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.67,1:59:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Always.\NOh, they always look at each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.63,1:59:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.94,2:00:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so lucky.\NWho else can we hug?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.06,2:00:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running out of people to hug.\NOh, hi, hi.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.09,2:00:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Side by side.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.85,2:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NGood to see you.
