Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.68,2:00:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.55,2:00:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They come tall, too, huh?\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.78,2:00:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.10,2:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to see you.\NGlad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.31,2:00:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NIt's wonderful to see all you people.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.68,2:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that saying go?\NThe mountain won't go to Muhammad.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.56,2:00:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Muhammad goes to them.\NOr is it the other way around?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:41.97,2:00:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.28,2:00:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I love you all.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.05,2:00:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, sir.\NVery special people.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:49.52,2:00:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why it's so special, but something.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.63,2:00:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about being Korean is wonderful.\NYou want a hug?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.10,2:01:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NI'll be good writer, like you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.60,2:01:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.48,2:01:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a handsome man.\NHandsome.
