Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.17,2:01:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.94,2:01:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for being here.\NI mean, what an honor to have people travel so long.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.69,2:01:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.31,2:01:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a long love.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.55,2:02:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.22,2:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloria in excelsis Deo, could you?\NYeah, let me see, where's my table at?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.57,2:02:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is a new cause that I don't know if it's a new or a new cause.\NYeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.43,2:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I guess,\Nwe don't know if it's a karma or whether it is a lesson,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:46.06,2:02:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, such as respecting life or,\Nor,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.43,2:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see where it is, but I think it's on the line.\NSo, you can't always say it's all the way there,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.18,2:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is done,\Nbut it's up to us to take the license and move forward,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.21,2:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe we have other people that have the same problem,\Nwe don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.09,2:03:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why I'm so, that's why I'm so,\Nmaybe I'm, I mean, I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.64,2:03:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about this?\NYes, that's what I thought,
Dialogue: 0,2:03:21.39,2:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have,\NI'm not sure, I'm not sure, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.25,2:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bowing to you.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.89,2:03:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bowing, we'll be bowing to you as we do on the New Year's Day.\NOh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.75,2:03:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As an expression of our love to you.\NOh, how very nice, how very nice.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:37.15,2:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe my way is that I love you.\NSusan, yeah, yeah, can we do this?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.43,2:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,.\N.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.43,2:04:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how beautiful.\NThanks to you, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.94,2:04:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen, I bless you all, in the name of the Lord, amen.\NI bless you all in the name of the Lord, amen.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.59,2:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So at this moment, last for eternity,\Nthis moment will always be.
